		{
			"item_armlet"		"~5-8 min
Your essential game-winning item. Cheap cost effective stats, armor and toggle ability in theory can make you unkillable early on."
			"item_heavens_halberd"		"~13-19 min
Additional HP and slow, but most importantly - miss chance and disarm, that allow you to continue showballing."
			"item_solar_crest"		"Can work as replacement or addition to halberd. Good against phys damage lineups."
			"item_dragon_lance"		"~15 min and on
Good stats and upgrade into hurricane pike, that may solve some mobility issues"
			"item_blink"		"Solve mobility issues with it or get to backlines of enemy formation (to kill enemies like sniper)"
			"item_black_king_bar"		"Your main threats are disables. If enemy has a lot of them, BKB may help you focus most important targets."
			"item_monkey_king_bar"		"High attack speed and pure damage. Disgusting."
			"item_guardian_greaves"		"Usually you don't even need to upgrade your boots. Altho, if you 100% sure you're not going to lategame, you may want to go for greaves because of ridiculous HP regen aura under 20% HP and strong aura for your team in general."
			"item_sphere"		"Usually BKB is better in terms of dealing with disables, but it may help against some scary stuff like DOOM"
